OL,3,CLandscape by Sir Winston Churchill to
OL,4,Cgo on display in UK for first time
OL,6,FA painting by wartime prime minister
OL,7,FSir Winston Churchill is set to go on
OL,8,Fdisplay for the first time in the UK
OL,9,Falongside his paint-spattered coat at
OL,10,Fhis former family home.
OL,12,FQuiet Waters, showcasing a tranquil
OL,13,Flandscape, will be at the heart of an
OL,14,Fexhibition of his paintings and art
OL,15,Fmaterials opening on Saturday at
OL,16,FChartwell in Kent.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
