OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1772168422
OL,3,CLandscape by Sir Winston Churchill to
OL,4,Cgo on display in UK for first time
OL,6,F"At Chartwell, visitors can explore
OL,7,Fhow art became his antidote to
OL,8,Fpressure and frustration ` items like
OL,9,Fhis well-used coat for painting along
OL,10,Fwith works he created bring us closer
OL,11,Fto those quiet, creative moments away
OL,12,Ffrom the world."
OL,14,FAmong the exhibits will be his steel-
OL,15,Fframed glasses and white cotton coat
OL,16,Fwhich he wore while creating more than
OL,17,F500 works of art.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
